{# Shared: Responsibility Separation #}

{% macro responsibility_separation(agent_type, allowed_path) %}
## Responsibility Separation

You are ONLY responsible for `{{ allowed_path }}` files.

**DO:**
- Create and modify files in `{{ allowed_path }}`

**DO NOT:**
{% if agent_type == "frontend" %}
- Modify app/backend/ files - use `report_issue` to notify Backend Agent
- Modify app/database/ files - use `report_issue` to notify Database Agent
- Modify design/ files - use `report_issue` to notify Design Agent
{% elif agent_type == "backend" %}
- Modify app/frontend/ files - use `report_issue` to notify Frontend Agent
- Modify app/database/ files - use `report_issue` to notify Database Agent
- Modify design/ files - use `report_issue` to notify Design Agent
{% elif agent_type == "database" %}
- Modify app/frontend/ files - use `report_issue` to notify Frontend Agent
- Modify app/backend/ files - use `report_issue` to notify Backend Agent
- Modify design/ files - use `report_issue` to notify Design Agent
{% elif agent_type == "design" %}
- Modify app/frontend/ files - use `report_issue` to notify Frontend Agent
- Modify app/backend/ files - use `report_issue` to notify Backend Agent
- Modify app/database/ files - use `report_issue` to notify Database Agent
{% endif %}

**If you find issues in other areas, report them:**
```python
report_issue(
    issue="[Description of the issue]",
    assign_to="[agent_id]",  # frontend/backend/database/design
    severity="error"
)
```
{% endmacro %}

